<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>MyBookShelf</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">MyBookShelf<sp/>is<sp/>an<sp/>open-source<sp/>Java<sp/>application<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>help<sp/>users<sp/>organize<sp/>and<sp/>track<sp/>their<sp/>personal<sp/>book<sp/>collection.<sp/>Whether<sp/>you&apos;re<sp/>an<sp/>avid<sp/>reader<sp/>or<sp/>a<sp/>casual<sp/>book<sp/>lover,<sp/>MyBookShelf<sp/>allows<sp/>you<sp/>to<sp/>manage<sp/>your<sp/>reading<sp/>list,<sp/>track<sp/>books<sp/>you&apos;ve<sp/>read,<sp/>and<sp/>plan<sp/>future<sp/>reads<sp/>all<sp/>in<sp/>one<sp/>place.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Features</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Book<sp/>Collection<sp/>Management**:<sp/>Add,<sp/>edit,<sp/>and<sp/>remove<sp/>books<sp/>from<sp/>your<sp/>collection.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Customizable<sp/>Categories**:<sp/>Organize<sp/>your<sp/>books<sp/>by<sp/>genres,<sp/>authors,<sp/>or<sp/>custom<sp/>tags.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Bookshelf<sp/>Overview**:<sp/>View<sp/>all<sp/>your<sp/>books<sp/>in<sp/>an<sp/>organized<sp/>and<sp/>easy-to-use<sp/>interface.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Search<sp/>Functionality**:<sp/>Quickly<sp/>search<sp/>for<sp/>books<sp/>by<sp/>title,<sp/>author,<sp/>or<sp/>category.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Reading<sp/>Goals**:<sp/>Set<sp/>and<sp/>track<sp/>your<sp/>reading<sp/>goals<sp/>throughout<sp/>the<sp/>year.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
